      • create

        public static <O> GuiHandler.GuiType<O> create(boolean carriesData)
        Create a new gui type. This requires a single call to both setContainerConstructor(org.cyclops.cyclopscore.client.gui.GuiHandler.IContainerConstructor) and setGuiConstructor(org.cyclops.cyclopscore.client.gui.GuiHandler.IGuiConstructor) for full initialization.
        Type Parameters:
        O - The type of temporary data passed to this gui type, can be Void.
        Parameters:
        carriesData - If this type requires additional data to be passed when the gui is opened.
        Returns:
        The new unique gui type instance.
